Any information we collect from you may be used in one of the following ways:

To transfer information to Professionals who provide their services through the app, always in accordance with confidentiality criteria.

To provide or transfer information to unrelated third parties in the following cases:
 2.1. At your request;
2.2. To comply with a legal obligation or a request from a government agency or court;
2.3. To investigate a possible crime, such as identity theft.
